        {
            "+content": "Tōya Senji is a high school boy who, despite excelling academically, sees himself as average because he constantly compares himself to his overachieving older brother. He desires to excel in something and become special. He encounters a long-absent classmate named Haito La Buffet, whom he considers exceptionally talented. He learns from her that she used a \"branch of reincarnation\" to claim talent from her \"past life,\" where she was the legendary swordsman Miyamoto Musashi, effectively becoming a \"Returner,\" a person reincarnated with their past life talent. Tōya also learns from Haito that there are other Returners who have more ambitious plans with their talents.",
